Text: Womens Election Rally with Jim McGreevey Kelly Ripa of Regis and Kelly and Andrew Shue of Melrose PlaceYou are invited to a Womens Election Rally with Democrat Jim McGreevey The next governor of New Jersey Come hear talk show host and actor Kelly Ripa of Regis and Kelly actor Andrew Shue of Melrose Place and other surprise guests Statewide Womens Election Rally Tuesday October th Paramus High School East Century Road pm The upcoming election will determine the direction that New Jersey takes over the next four years This event will provide an excellent opportunity to hear Jim McGreevey and local Democratic candidates articulate their vision for the future of our state For more information or to RSVP please contact Ana Lee or Christine at x or Directions From the West Take Rt East to Rt North to East Century Rd From the North Take Rt South to East Century Rd From the South Take West Local to Exit North to East Century Rd Democratic candidates across the state are unified under the Victory Statewide Coordinated Campaign Volunteer opportunities are available in each of our field offices in every county in the state For more information please reply to this email You have been sent this email because you or someone you know registered with our email distribution list If you have received this message in error please reply with UNSUBSCRIBE in the subject line using the email address you wish to remove PAID FOR BY NEW JERSEY DEMOCRATIC STATE COMMITTEE VICTORY
